{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"a006af0849ddcd4549138d10ccbf5d879da5acc578a90f8c5dee98d5874f4f50","slug":"internal-training","location":"/roadmap/qtclass/internal-training.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"内部教学制度改革","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":2}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/roadmap/qtclass/internal-training.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/roadmap/qtclass/internal-training.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"internal-training.md","url":"/internal-training-d81f2b445ea726344c0517e86222d961.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"建立和学习创始人相关的培训制度。要求全员“强制膜果”。","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"hJqJQA7Grt"}],"key":"a0mPKHWaZv"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这套制度的法理基础是，就是整个业务是高度围绕创始人进行，并且创始人已经大量地公开了 10 年内的思考，在各大账号和近期构建的第二大脑上面，因此团队已经有学习它的基础。秘书处已经验证了。","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"key":"kX5NZkpbrJ"}],"key":"BEn8tTPmom"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"内部教学","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"XX9seAABqc"}],"identifier":"id","label":"内部教学","html_id":"id","implicit":true,"key":"K7Mq5FSVIx"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"课程部门构建一个刁钻的问题清单，要求全员回答。","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"yhFFAeqNaD"}],"key":"JZDPL4tgqd"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"举例说明：","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"RX16vnmJzT"}],"key":"DZoeHb4cTF"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":14,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Q：为什么在群里发“应用经济学家的数据工程”？\nA：因为这是我们量潮数据的核心业务。最基础的要求是吸收经验，最主要的要求是了解客户自己能做到什么程度，多大程度可以替代我们，我们还有多少市场空间。","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"BCIM3wg6JW"}],"key":"VbmU5srUUA"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"用这些问题推动CEO助理训练营的教学工作推广到全体。把这些工作都列为业务活动。","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"key":"XnZwnr1AKh"}],"key":"r0Ac3bDLW0"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1},"end":{"line":18,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"类似的，也要求考核团队学习我给鲍讲的 Vibe Coding 的教学内容。","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1},"end":{"line":18,"column":1}},"key":"MRPfLMJXto"}],"key":"duBhcn15rL"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"首先从课程部门开始，他们不有效发现问题先惩罚他们。","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"QG3Af6M8kD"}],"key":"iJp1kx0D4O"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"交付问答清单到“course/ceo_assistant_bootcamp.md”","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"key":"Tw8eu7V5gC"}],"key":"JnwHFHTI0M"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1},"end":{"line":24,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"培训评估","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1},"end":{"line":24,"column":1}},"key":"OBPQ7cpzPB"}],"identifier":"id","label":"培训评估","html_id":"id-1","implicit":true,"key":"cXwDXyU6oJ"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"HR 部门要建立一个培训效果评估机制，不是围绕培训活动本身，而是看培训的问题是否解决。","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1},"end":{"line":26,"column":1}},"key":"eAkypGpHdl"}],"key":"VnQFUojsH0"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1},"end":{"line":28,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"比如：上面这个问题提出的动机是，发了资料没看到讨论，担心没有学习，因此想要构建深度学习的文化。","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1},"end":{"line":28,"column":1}},"key":"LlkmZexCdy"}],"key":"F16lWEtmok"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1},"end":{"line":30,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"交付评估清单到 quanttide-profile-of-business-entity 仓库的/hr/train/assessment.md。","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1},"end":{"line":30,"column":1}},"key":"cKEeG1I0DS"}],"key":"YaJdpUUqcK"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1},"end":{"line":32,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"组织管理","position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1},"end":{"line":32,"column":1}},"key":"wRklZyFwYO"}],"identifier":"id","label":"组织管理","html_id":"id-2","implicit":true,"key":"YctZCcfIxx"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1},"end":{"line":34,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这个改革在组织管理上的主要意图是重新划分课程部门和 HR 部门的职责边界。课程部门统一管理内部教学有利于给业务部门提供充分的素材；HR 部门转向评估效果，从秘书处的视角看待问题。","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1},"end":{"line":34,"column":1}},"key":"EjQwdjbgHa"}],"key":"u7SFWqLmsp"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"另外一个意图是推动绩效和薪资制度改革。从主要负责人事的课程部门和 HR 部门开始做起，先通过高压政策内化他们，再通过他们维持系统稳定。当他们开始自发维护这个制度时，则说明制度的成功运转。","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1},"end":{"line":36,"column":1}},"key":"CLYCvnc2ZB"}],"key":"frasTFfvxC"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"再另外一个意图是推动数字资产管理制度的改革，通过提交到公开工作简介，建立更开放透明的制度建设机制，并且训练团队参与开源体系建设。当团队内化了这个构建习惯，公司将会获得大量可以发布公众号的资料。","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":1},"end":{"line":38,"column":1}},"key":"ZwJpscF7DY"}],"key":"UtiApvJ8tN"}],"key":"ZxtOpEYBvF"}],"key":"Br2DJA7C7J"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}